575
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:51,960
That's such an old Internet gag.

576
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:53,679
I just wanted to hear it

577
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,639
from your own mouth,

578
00:34:55,719 --> 00:34:57,040
