579
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:58,080
That's all.

580
00:35:00,360 --> 00:35:01,680
You really are adorable.

581
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:03,760
Cheers.

582
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:10,280
There won't be any "better you and I."

583
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:12,280
